ActCanada Mortgage and Housing Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Employment and Social Development of NAVJEET (BOB) DHILLON of Calgary, Alberta, to be a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation, to hold office during pleasure, on a part-time basis, for a term of four years, in the place of Michael Gendron.
